# aiaio (AI-AI-O)

A lightweight, privacy-focused web UI for interacting with AI models. Supports both local and remote LLM deployments through OpenAI-compatible APIs.

![Screenshot](https://github.com/abhishekkrthakur/aiaio/blob/main/ui.png?raw=true)

## Features

- üåì Dark/Light mode support
- üíæ Local SQLite database for conversation storage
- üìÅ File upload and processing (images, documents, etc.)
- ‚öôÔ∏è Configurable model parameters through UI
- üîí Privacy-focused (all data stays local)
- üì± Responsive design for mobile/desktop
- üé® Syntax highlighting for code blocks
- üìã One-click code block copying
- üîÑ Real-time conversation updates
